	Mizmor shir leyom hashabbat./PR

	Tov lehodot ladonay	ulzamer leshimeh/±a elyon./PR

	Lehagid ba/UNbo/XXker h/±as/UNde/XXh/±a	veòemunateh/±a baleylot./PR

