/ITSome congregations recite /MDAshrey/XX (Psalm 145, page 429) here./PR

/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. How often it feels that the chaos in our world -- and the
chaotic feelings in our hearts -- could overwhelm us! The central Jewish
article of faith that God is one and that the world is therefore one, that
the world makes sense, stands as an assertion that the forces of chaos will
not ultimately prevail. The floods raise up torrential waves, but we listen
for the one reality that can overwhelm the mighty waters.    /SC/XXD.A.T./XX/PR

